eqlReplPartnerTestTable.description: EqualLogic-Persistent ReplPartnerTestTable. This table contains replication partner test information. TimeoutCreate:60 TimeoutDelete:60

eqlReplPartnerTestEntry.name: eqlReplPartnerTestEntry
eqlReplPartnerTestEntry.description: An entry (row) containing replication partner test info.

eqlReplPartnerTestIPAddrStatus.name: eqlReplPartnerTestIPAddrStatus
eqlReplPartnerTestIPAddrStatus.description: The replication partner IP address test status.

eqlReplPartnerTestAuthStatus.name: eqlReplPartnerTestAuthStatus
eqlReplPartnerTestAuthStatus.description: The replication partner authentication test status.

eqlReplPartnerTestMajorVersion.name: eqlReplPartnerTestMajorVersion
eqlReplPartnerTestMajorVersion.description: This field specifies the Major part of the lowest member software version of the remote replication site group.

eqlReplPartnerTestMinorVersion.name: eqlReplPartnerTestMinorVersion
eqlReplPartnerTestMinorVersion.description: This field specifies the Minor part of the lowest member software version of the remote replication site group.

eqlReplPartnerTestMaintVersion.name: eqlReplPartnerTestMaintVersion
eqlReplPartnerTestMaintVersion.description: This field specifies the Maintenance part of the lowest member software version of the remote replication site group.

eqlReplPartnerTestDelegatedSpace.name: eqlReplPartnerTestDelegatedSpace
eqlReplPartnerTestDelegatedSpace.description: This field indicates the total delegated space for the partners. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlReplPartnerTestDelegatedSpaceUsed.name: eqlReplPartnerTestDelegatedSpaceUsed
eqlReplPartnerTestDelegatedSpaceUsed.description: This field indicates the total delegated space used by partners. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlReplPartnerTestTimestamp.name: eqlReplPartnerTestTimestamp
eqlReplPartnerTestTimestamp.description: This field specifies the date/time when replication partner test was started. Time is represented as the time in seconds since 00:00:00 UTC, 1970-01-01.
